ISLAMABAD, Jul 06 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Senator Shibli Faraz Monday said the protest following suspension of Channel-24 licence was very unfortunate as respecting law was the duty of all Pakistanis.
Tagging the notification of Pakistan Electronic Media Regulatory Authority, the minister, in a tweet, said disregard of all notices had resulted in suspension of the licence of Channel 24.\
